title: United Kingdom Imports of Ships Boats & Floating Structures
description: Imports of Ships, Boats & Floating Structures in the United Kingdom decreased to 32.17 GBP Million in September from 51.84 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Ships, Boats & Floating Structures in the United Kingdom averaged 60.02 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 837.88 GBP Million in October of 2017 and a record low of 5.57 GBP Million in October of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Ships, Boats & Floating Structures.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
